What you need to know:

The proprietor of Astorian Grand Hotel in Naivasha, Stephen Mungai Aston, said his facility has been fully booked ahead of WRC Safari Rally due June 24-27 this yearMungai revealed that he will be recalling all the workers, who had been sent home after the facilities were closed due to Covid-19 pandemicPanorama Hotel General Manager, Sammy Mugo, admitted that hosting the event has been a turning point for hoteliers